<style>
  .mainEvent::-webkit-scrollbar{
    width:0;
  }
</style>
<div data-action="admins">
<p>Hello</p>
</div>
<div class="mainEvent max-w-screen-xl h-full overflow-y-scroll mx-auto">
    <div class="mx-auto">
      <details class="open:bg-white dark:open:bg-slate-900 open:ring-1 open:ring-black/5 p-4 dark:open:ring-white/10 open:shadow-lg  rounded-lg">
        <summary class="text-3xl font-bold flex leading-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold select-none">
          <span>Актуальные статьи</span>
          <svg class="w-8 ps-2 pb-1 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="#000000"><g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g><g id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></g><g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier"> <title></title> <g id="Complete"> <g id="info-circle"> <g> <circle cx="12" cy="12" data-name="--Circle" fill="none" id="_--Circle" r="10" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></circle> <line fill="none" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" x1="12" x2="12" y1="12" y2="16"></line> <line fill="none" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" x1="12" x2="12" y1="8" y2="8"></line> </g> </g> </g> </g></svg>

        </summary>
        <div class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 з-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <p>Статьи - это более глубокие и детальные материалы, которые объясняют или анализируют тему. Такие материалы могут содержать дополнительную информацию, исследования, интервью, мнения экспертов и т.д. Колонка "Статьи" обычно предназначена для более долгосрочных материалов, которые дают более глубокое понимание темы и позволяют читателю получить более полное представление о ней.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
    <main class="mt-5">
      <div class="block md:flex md:space-x-2 px-2 lg:p-0">
        <a
          class="mb-4 md:mb-0 w-full md:w-2/3 relative rounded inline-block"
          style="height: 24em;"
          href="/articles/<%= @articles[0].id %>"
        >
          <div class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 w-full h-full z-10"
            style="background-image: linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,rgba(0,0,0,.7));"></div>
          <img src="<%= url_for(@articles[0].header) %>" class="absolute opacity-75 left-0 top-0 w-full h-full rounded z-0 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-4 absolute bottom-0 left-0 z-20">
            <% @articles[0].tag_list.each do |tag|%>
              <span class="px-4 py-1 bg-black text-gray-200 inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-2"><%= tag %></span>
            <%end%>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-gray-100 leading-tight">
              <%= @articles[0].title %>
            </h2>
            <div class="flex mt-3">
              <img src="<%= url_for(@articles[0].user.avatar) %>"
                class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full mr-2 object-cover" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-200 text-sm"> <%= @articles[0].user.login %> </p>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-400 text-xs"> <%= l( @articles[0].created_at, format: :short)%> </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="w-full md:w-1/3 relative rounded"
          style="height: 24em;"
          href="./articles/<%= @articles[1].id %>"
        >
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-full h-full z-10"
            style="background-image: linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,rgba(0,0,0,.7));"></div>
          <img src="<%= url_for(@articles[1].header) %>" class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-full h-full rounded opacity-75 z-0 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-4 absolute bottom-0 left-0 z-20">
            <% @articles[1].tag_list.each do |tag|%>
              <span class="px-4 py-1 bg-black text-gray-200 inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-2"><%= tag %></span>
            <%end%>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-100 leading-tight"> <%= @articles[1].title %></h2>
            <div class="flex mt-3">
              <img
                src="<%= url_for(@articles[1].user.avatar) %>"
                class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full mr-2 object-cover" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-200 text-sm"> <%= @articles[1].user.login %> </p>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-400 text-xs"> <%= l( @articles[1].created_at, format: :short)%> </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <div class="block lg:flex lg:space-x-2 px-2 lg:p-0 mt-10 mb-10">

        <div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <a href="/articles/new">
              <button class="text-xl border-2 border-emerald-500 p-2 font-bold text-emerald-500 shadow mb-2 rounded-lg ">
                Написать статью
              </button>
            </a>
            <a href="/article/find/">
              <button class="text-xl border-2 border-blue-500 p-2 font-bold text-blue-500 shadow mb-2 rounded-lg ">
                Перейти в поиск
              </button>
            </a>
            <a href="/article/selected">
              <button class="text-xl border-2 border-yellow-500 p-2 font-bold text-yellow-500 shadow mb-2 rounded-lg ">
                Перейти в избранное
              </button>
            </a>

          </div>

          <% @articles.each do |a| %>
            <div class="w-full ">

              <a class="block rounded w-full lg:flex mb-10"
                href="/articles/<%= a.id %>"
              >
                <div
                  class="h-48 lg:w-48 flex-none bg-cover text-center overflow-hidden "
                  style="background-image: url('<%= url_for(a.header) %>')"
                  title="deit is very important"
                >
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded px-4 flex flex-col leading-normal">
                  <div class="">
                    <div class="mt-2 text-gray-700 font-bold text-2xl mb-2">
                      <%= a.title %>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
                      <%= a.body[0..150] + "..."%>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex mt-3">
                    <img src="<%= url_for(a.user.avatar) %>"
                      class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full mr-2 object-cover" />
                    <div>
                      <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 text-sm capitalize"> <%= a.user.login %> </p>
                      <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs"> <%= l(a.created_at, format: :short)%> </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>


        <!-- right sidebar -->
        <div class="w-1/2 px-3">
          <!-- topics -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h5 class="font-bold text-lg uppercase text-gray-700 px-1 mb-2"> Популярные тэги </h5>
            <ul>
              <li class="px-1 py-4 border-b border-t border-white hover:border-gray-200 transition duration-300">
                <a href="/articles/tag/<%= @popular_tags[0] %>" class="flex items-center text-gray-600 cursor-pointer">
                  <span class="inline-block h-4 w-4 bg-green-300 mr-3"></span>
                  <%= @popular_tags[0].name %>
                  <span class="text-gray-500 ml-auto">Статей: <%= @popular_tags[0].count %></span>
                  <i class='text-gray-500 bx bx-right-arrow-alt ml-1'></i>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="px-1 py-4 border-b border-t border-white hover:border-gray-200 transition duration-300">
                <a href="/articles/tag/<%= @popular_tags[0] %>" class="flex items-center text-gray-600 cursor-pointer">
                  <span class="inline-block h-4 w-4 bg-indigo-300 mr-3"></span>
                  <%= @popular_tags[1].name %>
                  <span class="text-gray-500 ml-auto">Статей: <%= @popular_tags[0].count %></span>
                  <i class='text-gray-500 bx bx-right-arrow-alt ml-1'></i>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="px-1 py-4 border-b border-t border-white hover:border-gray-200 transition duration-300">
                <a href="/articles/tag/<%= @popular_tags[0] %>" class="flex items-center text-gray-600 cursor-pointer">
                  <span class="inline-block h-4 w-4 bg-yellow-300 mr-3"></span>
                  <%= @popular_tags[2].name %>
                  <span class="text-gray-500 ml-auto">Статей: <%= @popular_tags[0].count %></span>
                  <i class='text-gray-500 bx bx-right-arrow-alt ml-1'></i>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="px-1 py-4 border-b border-t border-white hover:border-gray-200 transition duration-300">
                <a href="/articles/tag/<%= @popular_tags[0] %>" class="flex items-center text-gray-600 cursor-pointer">
                  <span class="inline-block h-4 w-4 bg-blue-300 mr-3"></span>
                  <%= @popular_tags[3].name %>
                  <span class="text-gray-500 ml-auto">Статей: <%= @popular_tags[0].count %></span>
                  <i class='text-gray-500 bx bx-right-arrow-alt ml-1'></i>
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- divider -->
          <div class="border border-dotted"></div>

          <!-- subscribe -->
          <div class="p-1 mt-4 mb-4">
            <h5 class="font-bold text-lg uppercase text-gray-700 mb-2"> Оформите подписку </h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Упростите получение интересных для вас статей в пару кликов
            </p>
            <input placeholder="Ваш почта"
              class="text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 rounded-t hover:outline-none p-2 w-full mt-4 border" />
            <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-gray-200 rounded-b w-full capitalize tracking-wide">
              Подписаться
            </button>
          </div>

          <!-- divider -->
          <div class="border border-dotted"></div>

        </div>

      </div>
    </main>
    <!-- main ends here -->

    <!-- footer -->
    <footer class="border-t mt-32 pt-12 pb-32 px-4 lg:px-0">
      <div class="flex">

        <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/4">
          <h6 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Company</h6>
          <ul>
            <li> <a href="" class="block text-gray-600 py-2">Team</a> </li>
            <li> <a href="" class="block text-gray-600 py-2">About us</a> </li>
            <li> <a href="" class="block text-gray-600 py-2">Press</a> </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/4">
          <h6 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Content</h6>
          <ul>
            <li> <a href="" class="block text-gray-600 py-2">Blog</a> </li>
            <li> <a href="" class="block text-gray-600 py-2">Privacy Policy</a> </li>
            <li> <a href="" class="block text-gray-600 py-2">Terms & Conditions</a> </li>
            <li> <a href="" class="block text-gray-600 py-2">Documentation</a> </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
